#

Fusilli with Tomato Basil Sauce

25 min
$8.5
450 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianNut-Free

Cuisine:

Italian

Course:

Main

Tags:

PastaQuick MealItalian

Description

A delightful pasta dish with a vibrant tomato basil sauce that’s simple yet bursting with flavor.

Ingredients

  • fusilli pasta: 8 ounces
  • canned crushed tomatoes: 14 ounces
  • fresh basil leaves: 1/2 cup
  • garlic: 2 cloves
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • parmesan cheese: 1/4 cup
  • salt: 1 teaspoon
  • black pepper: 1/2 teaspoon
